# Agent Instructions

## Setup Commands

### Backend (Python)

- **Install:** `pip install -r requirements.txt`
- **Dev:** `fastapi dev main.py`
- **Test:** `pytest`

### Frontend (React)

- **Install:** `npm install`
- **Dev:** `npm run dev`
- **Build:** `npm run build`

---

## Code Style

### Python

- PEP 8 compliance
- Black formatter
- Type Hints (mandatory)

### React

- Functional Components
- Hooks
- ESLint standard
- Follow patterns in `@context/knowledge/patterns/` (when created)

---

## Context Files to Load

Before starting work, load:

| Priority | File | Description |
|----------|------|-------------|
| Always | `@context/intent/project-intent.md` | Project intent |
| High | `@context/decisions/001-tech-stack.md` | Defined stack |
| Medium | `@context/decisions/*.md` | Other relevant decisions |

